(41, 1, 41, 58, 4, 15, 15, NULL, 'Compassion and Infirmities Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of Jesus'' compassion and his ability to empathize with human suffering. Both passages emphasize being ''touched'' by the feelings of infirmities, illustrating Jesus'' deep understanding of human struggles.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
