(41, 1, 41, 41, 6, 34, 34, 'moved with compassion', 'Compassion of Jesus', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' compassion as a driving force behind his actions. In Mark 1:41, his compassion leads him to heal, while in Mark 6:34, it motivates him to teach the people.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
