(41, 1, 42, 43, 15, 3, 3, NULL, 'Cleansing Through Spoken Word', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of cleansing through spoken words. In Mark, the leper is cleansed immediately after Jesus speaks, while in John, Jesus indicates that his words also bring about a state of cleanliness.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
