(41, 1, 42, 41, 1, 31, 31, 'immediately', 'Healing and Immediate Response', 'Both passages emphasize immediate healing, as seen in the phrases ''immediately the leprosy departed'' and ''immediately the fever left her.'' This connection highlights the power of Jesus'' touch in restoring health.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
